node.text: @barbie Color Reveal dolls deliver an unboxing experience like no other! Each doll has four bags to discover a long-haired wig, a skirt, a pair of shoes and a small sponge. Highly collectible, limited-edition Street Sharks ahead! All three are packed with premium deco, unique accessories, and a boatload of nostalgia! This special moment in #streetsharks history is only available at @mattelcreations.

node.text: There’s nothing like a game of @uno to bring people together (before temporarily tearing them apart 😊). In June, during It Gets Better: A Digital Pride Experience, Mattel’s Herschel Canton-Hudson played a game of UNO with leaders and friends of the @itgetsbetter Project. It’s just one example of how meaningful conversations can happen over a game of UNO. #Pride month may be over, but inclusivity and unity are always important. Mattel is proud to have partnered with the It Gets Better Project to create UNO Play with Pride and to help support its mission of empowering LGBTQ+ youth.
